main event: Several bright lights were observed in the sky over Kadena, Okinawa on September 6, 1959.
interesting points: The lights moved in different directions,One light disappeared very quickly while others continued moving together, The lights were visible only when probable weather effects on radar were taken into account, The visual sighting lasted for approximately 5-8 minutes, The sighting was reported by military personnel at Kadena Air Base.
witness description: Military personnel from Kadena Air Base
